k <- 10
kfolds_driver <- trainControl(method = "cv", number = k , repeats = 10, verboseIter = T)
Warning: `repeats` has no meaning for this resampling method.
#model1 <- dataset %>%
#  lm(formula= median_house_value ~ .)

             data= dataset,
             trControl = kfolds_driver,
